trans-unit.source:
This files are uses as favicons for the website.
Only these filenames are supported: ([W] == width, [H] == height)
* favicon.ico * favicon-[W]x[H].png * apple-touch-icon.png * apple-touch-icon-precomposed.png * android-chrome-[W]x[H].png * mstile-[W]x[H].png * safari-pinned-tab.svg
